These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, engineer, freelancer, bartender
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, lacrosse, baseball, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the engineer##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the freelancer##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the librarian##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the engineer##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 8. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Job   | engineer | librarian    | bartender   | freelancer    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Sport     | lacrosse       | water-polo | surfing  | baseball      |

