.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, pear, broccoli, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, mystery
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, salsa, disco, funk
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person eating pear##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
11. the fan of country is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Food      | pear       | apricot | corn     | broccoli     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | crime       | mystery | martial-arts |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Music-Genre     | funk | disco     | country     | salsa       |

