.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, pumpkin, radish
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, mirinda, 7up
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, turtle
 1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking mirinda##2
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person playing go is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | pumpkin      | plum   | apricot |
| Game   | bridge | go | mah-jongg | poker  |
| Beverage   | sprite   | mirinda         | iced-tea  | 7up  |
| Pet           | pony      | dog          | turtle | lizard  |

