 1. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the accountant is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the project-manager##2
 4. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
 9. the doctor is on the left or right of the russian##3
10. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Game          | whist    | go        | canasta     | scrabble          |
| Job           | analyst | doctor        | accountant | project-manager |
| Nationality   | russian    | brazilian     | indian      | american        |

