.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, egyptian, thai
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, december, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the american is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the egyptian##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
13. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | egyptian   | thai      | american | indonesian     |
| Birthday           | november   | march  | june        | december |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | zombie     | thriller      | disaster   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

