.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, boat, bus, subway
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, coral, lavender, grey
 1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the person who likes grey is the person driving the ship##1
 3. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
 7. the social-worker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | ship | bus  | subway    | boat       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Color   | grey      | lavender    | coral        | fuchsia |

 